 derived from failure, error and disgust.  Laura Duffy holds a Bachelor of Fine Arts with First Class Honours from Whiti O Rehua, Massey University. Since graduating she has worked on projects with multiple artist-run spaces and institutions throughout Aotearoa as well Australia, China and Japan. Previously, Laura has been a facilitator of artist-run initiative MEANWHILE (2017-2019). Laura is currently featured on Circuit Artist Film and Video Aotearoa and RM's Women's Moving Image Archive.\n\n[Sourced from artist website: https://lauraduffy.myportfolio.com/bio 27 Oct 2021]", "biography_author": null, "date_of_biography": "2025-03-12T02:07:49.061546+11:00", "external_links": [], "uuid": "002f2108-00ac-44dd-b251-1daf913f6399", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "40089", "external_references": [], "date_modified": "2025-03-12T02:07:49.061924+11:00"}, {"id": 86131, "name": "Tehree Gordon", "roles_in_work": [{"id": 3110404, "title": "Why?", "work_id": 119744, "role": "creator", "role_id": 968, "is_primary": true}], "also_known_as": "", "date_of_birth": "", "date_of_death": "", "genders": [{"id": 5, "name": "Female", "slug": "female"}], "languages": [], "places_of_operation": [], "biography": "", "biography_author": null, "date_of_biography": "2023-05-09T17:42:03.504113+10:00", "external_links": [], "uuid": "01b5af01-d5ca-4df2-bca8-be7df63fbf0a", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "39558", "external_references": [], "date_modified": "2025-12-17T14:37:12.073136+11:00"}, {"id": 86122, "name": "Kat Mew", "roles_in_work": [{"id": 3099054, "title": "She swallowed the spider to catch the fly", "work_id": 109444, "role": "creator", "role_id": 968, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 3099048, "title": "Adventures of cyberkid", "work_id": 109443, "role": "creator", "role_id": 968, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 3099072, "title": "Owed to Jack Kerouac and my friends", "work_id": 109450, "role": "creator", "role_id": 968, "is